title: Eric Clapton - 2014 New Orleans Jazz Fest 1080p AC3 mkv
description:
The 2014 New Orleans Jazz & Heritage Festival was held April 25 thru May 4, 2014. The concert was supposedly broadcast live in its entirety by AXS.TV. According to the published schedule Eric Clapton performed as the closing act on the third day, Sunday, April 27. Eric Clapton was scheduled to play a long set of 1 hour 50 minutes duration. However, AXS.tv broadcast only 23 minutes of the set.

This video was produced by a 3-pass encode at a bit rate sufficient to keep in perfect sync with the audio. The audio has been kept at the very high quality of the original broadcast. It can really give your high-watt sound system a workout. So if you got it then pump the volume and enjoy.

Video format: MKV, AVC (H.264), 1920x1080 (16:9), 8000 Kbps at 29.97 fps
Audio format: AC-3 6-channels, Dolby 5.1, 640 Kbps, 48 KHz.
Duration: 23 minutes
